Titolo: ATV Simulator

Anno: 1987

Descrizione: ATV Simulator (also known as All Terrain Vehicle Simulation) is a computer game released for the ZX Spectrum, Commodore 64 and Amstrad CPC by Codemasters.
The goal of the game is to drive an ATV through various courses which must be completed within the time limit without running out of fuel.  If a player crashes the ATV, they can move their man to get back into the vehicle, but it will cost time to do so. If a player runs out time or fuel, the game is over.

Genere: Sports simulation

Valutazione: N/A
